The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades adorned with colorful advertisements that add a splash of vibrancy to the scene. The street itself is lined with trees, their lush greenery contrasting with the concrete structures. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in many cities. The sun shines brightly in the top left corner of the image, casting long shadows and illuminating the scene with a warm glow.
